						               													<description>QUIZ Schalke 04 &amp;ldquo;Blue and white, how I love you&amp;rdquo;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Prove your passion now with the QUIZ Schalke 04! &amp;#10;All information about the club and its players is brought together here. &amp;#10;So kick off and let's go! If your greatest passion is soccer and you don't miss a game of the Royal Blues, then we have just the right thing for 2 players or teams from 6 years of age. Because in this QUIZ your memory will be put to the test twice with a total of 500 questions. &amp;#10;In the first round, each player or team draws five cards. Read the first question out to you one at a time. If only one of you has the correct answer, he receives the card. If both are correct, it continues until one answers the question incorrectly. If both players or teams do not know the answer to the first question or answer all five questions correctly, the cards land in the middle. Now you continue with the next card and if you can answer the question correctly while your opponent is wrong, you will receive the stack of cards from the middle. Whoever has collected three cards wins the first round. In the second round you shuffle the ten cards you have already played, distribute them again among you and play the cards again. If your little head is not only an absolute ace in the header, but was also able to remember most of the first round and collect three cards again, you win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
